org.oasis.openc2.lycan.targets

Class OpenC2Target

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.oasis.openc2.lycan.utilities.OpenC2BaseSection
      • org.oasis.openc2.lycan.utilities.OpenC2BaseTypeSection<TargetType>
        • org.oasis.openc2.lycan.targets.OpenC2Target
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Artifact, DomainName, Ipv4Addr

    public class OpenC2Target
extends OpenC2BaseTypeSection<TargetType>
    Generic implementation of a OpenC2 messages target section. While this class can be used raw, it's intended that the class would be extended for each target type where the extended class would provide convenience methods for the allowed specifiers based on the spec.
